Job Details - Experienced Early Years Teachers Wanted in the UAE
Experienced Early Years Teachers Wanted in the UAE
Donderdag 1 mei 2014
Description
Teachanywhere is seeking 2 Early Years Teachers for a rapidly growing Primary school in Abu Dhabi which provides the American curriculum to local Emirati students. Currently catering for students from KG to Grade 6 the current campus will relocate to purpose built modern site in August 2014 and will have the capacity to expand to G12 in future years.
Requirements:    Bachelors of Early Years Education or equivalent supported with a relevant teaching license /  certificate. All degrees MUST have been issued in either UK,Ireland,Australia/New Zealand/Canada/US & South Africa ONLY.
Package:
Tax free salary subject to negotiation
Free Furnished Accommodation
Annual Flights
Medical Insurance
If you wish to apply for this exciting opportunity, please contact your local Teachanywhere recruiter, Katie on ks@teachanywhere.com
Job Reference:KS/Yasat
Position Type:Permanent
Sector:Education, Training & Library
Location:Abu Dhabi, Abu Dhabi, United Arab Emirates
Contact:Katie Smith, Contact Code: KS/Yasat, Randstad, Teach Anywhere, Australia
